[SN]TITLE[SN]
Maghaberry Prison: Ford says inmates must help ease tensions

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Inmates at Maghaberry Prison must accept their part in lowering tensions and ending intimidation of jail staff, Justice Minister David Ford has said.

